title: Usage of top level domains for websites 2019
summary: This statistic presents a ranking of the most-backed kickstarter projects in the united kingdom ( uk ) in 2014 , by number of speakers . The majority of 2018 , it was found that 13.4 percent of visits were directed to market leader zillow . A 2016 survey found online websites to be the most popular information channels consulted when looking for a house to purchase in the united , even ahead of real estate agents .
gold: This statistic gives information on the distribution of worldwide top level domains as of November 2019 . As of that month , 48 percent of all global websites used a .com top-level domain . A further 3.5 percent used a .net TLD .
